.TH "nvme_init_get_log_discovery" 9 "nvme_init_get_log_discovery" "April 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nvme_init_get_log_discovery \- Initialize passthru command for Discovery
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" nvme_init_get_log_discovery
.BI "(struct libnvme_passthru_cmd *cmd "  ","
.BI "__u64 lpo "  ","
.BI "void *log "  ","
.BI "__u32 len "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "cmd" 12
Passthru command to use
.IP "lpo" 12
Offset of this log to retrieve
.IP "log" 12
User address to store the discovery log
.IP "len" 12
The allocated size for this portion of the log
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Initializes the passthru command buffer for the Get Log command with
LID value NVME_LOG_LID_DISCOVERY
